            "title": "Updating a variable",
            "id": 126281,
            "contentType": "interactive",
            "images": [],
            "interactiveContent": "<!DOCTYPE html ><html><body><p>Já vimos que variáveis <code>var</code>, ao contrário de <code>let</code>, podem mudar e atualizar os valores que armazenam.</p><p>Use o sinal <code>=</code> para mudar o valor em <code>status</code> de <code>\"Watching Netflix\"</code> para <code>\"Relaxing at the beach\"</code>.</p><code version=\"2\" codelang=\"swift\" name=\"main.swift\" visible-if=\"always\"><content><text value=\"var\" class=\"keyword\" /><text value=\" currentStatus = \" /><text value=\"&quot;Watching Netflix&quot;\" class=\"string\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"currentStatus = \" /><text value=\"&quot;Relaxing at the beach&quot;\" class=\"string\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"print\" class=\"built_in\" /><text value=\"(currentStatus)\" /><text type=\"break\" /></content><interactions><interaction type=\"fillTheGap\" isDefault=\"true\"><options><option startIndex=\"53\" endIndex=\"54\" /><option correct=\"false\"><content><text value=\":\" /></content></option></options></interaction></interactions><output><content><text value=\"Relaxing at the beach\" /></content></output></code><p visible-if=\"wrong\">Certifique-se de escolher <code>=</code>.</p></body></html>"
          },
          {
            "title": "As often as we want",
            "id": 126282,
            "contentType": "interactive",
            "images": [],
            "interactiveContent": "<!DOCTYPE html ><html><body><p>Podemos atualizar variáveis <code>var</code> quantas vezes quisermos.</p><p>Tente você mesmo: altere o valor de <code>currentStatus</code> para <code>\"Reading\"</code>.</p><code version=\"2\" codelang=\"swift\" name=\"main.swift\" visible-if=\"always\"><content><text value=\"var\" class=\"keyword\" /><text value=\" currentStatus = \" /><text value=\"&quot;Watching Netflix&quot;\" class=\"string\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"currentStatus = \" /><text value=\"&quot;Relaxing at the Beach&quot;\" class=\"string\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"print\" class=\"built_in\" /><text value=\"(currentStatus)\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"currentStatus = \" /><text value=\"&quot;Reading&quot;\" class=\"string\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"print\" class=\"built_in\" /><text value=\"(currentStatus)\" /><text type=\"break\" /></content><interactions><interaction type=\"fillTheGap\" isDefault=\"true\"><options><option startIndex=\"101\" endIndex=\"114\" /><option startIndex=\"115\" endIndex=\"116\" /><option startIndex=\"117\" endIndex=\"126\" /></options></interaction></interactions><output><content><text value=\"Relaxing at the Beach\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"Reading\" /></content></output></code><p visible-if=\"wrong\">Certifique-se de escolher <code>currentStatus</code> seguido de <code>=</code> e finalmente <code>\"Reading\"</code>.</p></body></html>"
          },
          {
            "title": "Setting with other variables",
            "id": 126283,
            "contentType": "interactive",
            "images": [],
            "interactiveContent": "<!DOCTYPE html ><html><body><p>Também podemos dar às variáveis os valores de outras variáveis, definindo uma variável para a outra.</p><p>Atribua à variável <code>currentStatus</code> o valor de <code>defaultStatus</code>.</p><code version=\"2\" codelang=\"swift\" name=\"main.swift\" visible-if=\"always\"><content><text value=\"let\" class=\"keyword\" /><text value=\" defaultStatus = \" /><text value=\"&quot;Hi there!&quot;\" class=\"string\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"var\" class=\"keyword\" /><text value=\" currentStatus = \" /><text value=\"&quot;Playing football&quot;\" class=\"string\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"currentStatus = defaultStatus\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"print\" class=\"built_in\" /><text value=\"(currentStatus)\" /></content><interactions><interaction type=\"fillTheGap\" isDefault=\"true\"><options><option correct=\"false\"><content><text value=\"&quot;Playing football&quot;\" /></content></option><option startIndex=\"88\" endIndex=\"101\" /></options></interaction></interactions><output><content><text value=\"Hi there!\" /></content></output></code><p visible-if=\"wrong\">Certifique-se de escolher <code>defaultStatus</code>.</p></body></html>"
          },
          {
            "title": "Last value",
            "id": 126284,
            "contentType": "interactive",
            "images": [],
            "interactiveContent": "<!DOCTYPE html ><html><body><p>Quando atualizamos uma variável, ela esquece seu valor anterior.</p><p>Exiba a variável <code>currentStatus</code> quando ela estiver definida como <code>\"Playing football\"</code> e quando estiver definida como <code>\"Walking the dog\"</code>.</p><code version=\"2\" codelang=\"swift\" name=\"main.swift\" visible-if=\"always\"><content><text value=\"var\" class=\"keyword\" /><text value=\" currentStatus = \" /><text value=\"&quot;Playing football&quot;\" class=\"string\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"print\" class=\"built_in\" /><text value=\"(currentStatus)\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"currentStatus = \" /><text value=\"&quot;Walking the dog&quot;\" class=\"string\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"print\" class=\"built_in\" /><text value=\"(currentStatus)\" /><text type=\"break\" /></content><interactions><interaction type=\"fillTheGap\" isDefault=\"true\"><options><option startIndex=\"45\" endIndex=\"58\" /><option startIndex=\"101\" endIndex=\"114\" /><option correct=\"false\"><content><text value=\"var currentStatus\" /></content></option></options></interaction></interactions><output><content><text value=\"Playing football\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"Walking the dog\" /></content></output></code><p visible-if=\"wrong\">Certifique-se de escolher <code>currentStatus</code> seguido de <code>currentStatus</code>.</p></body></html>"
