          {
            "title": "Adding string values",
            "id": 126293,
            "contentType": "interactive",
            "images": [],
            "interactiveContent": "<!DOCTYPE html ><html><body><p>Podemos adicionar valores de string juntos com um sinal de <code>+</code>.</p><p>Adicione os valores <code>\"Followers:\"</code> e <code>\"55\"</code> juntos.</p><code name=\"main.swift\" version=\"2\" codelang=\"swift\"><content><text value=\"&quot;Followers:&quot;\" class=\"string\" /><text value=\" + \" /><text value=\"&quot;55&quot;\" class=\"string\" /></content><interactions><interaction type=\"fillTheGap\" isDefault=\"true\"><options><option correct=\"false\"><content><text value=\"-\" /></content></option><option startIndex=\"13\" endIndex=\"14\" /></options></interaction></interactions></code><p visible-if=\"wrong\">Certifique-se de escolher <code>+</code>.</p></body></html>"
          },
          {
            "title": "Displaying expressions",
            "id": 126294,
            "contentType": "interactive",
            "images": [],
            "interactiveContent": "<!DOCTYPE html ><html><body><p>Chamamos a adição de valores de string de <strong>expressão</strong> porque ela cria um único valor de string.</p><p>Adicione a expressão entre os parênteses de <code>print()</code>.</p><code name=\"main.swift\" version=\"2\" codelang=\"swift\"><content><text value=\"print\" class=\"built_in\" /><text value=\"(\" /><text value=\"&quot;Followers:&quot;\" class=\"string\" /><text value=\" + \" /><text value=\"&quot;55&quot;\" class=\"string\" /><text value=\")\" /></content><interactions><interaction type=\"fillTheGap\" isDefault=\"true\"><options><option startIndex=\"6\" endIndex=\"18\" /><option startIndex=\"19\" endIndex=\"20\" /><option startIndex=\"21\" endIndex=\"25\" /></options></interaction></interactions><output><content><text value=\"Followers:55\" /></content></output></code><p visible-if=\"wrong\">Certifique-se de escolher <code>\"Followers:\"</code> seguido de <code>+</code> e finalmente <code>\"55\"</code>.</p></body></html>"
          },
          {
            "title": "Expressions with variables",
            "id": 126295,
            "contentType": "interactive",
            "images": [],
            "interactiveContent": "<!DOCTYPE html ><html><body><p>Quando expressões contêm variáveis, elas usam os valores nas variáveis.</p><p>Crie uma expressão que adicione o valor <code>\"Followers:\"</code> e a variável <code>followers</code> juntos.</p><code name=\"main.swift\" version=\"2\" codelang=\"swift\"><content><text value=\"let\" class=\"keyword\" /><text value=\" followers = \" /><text value=\"&quot;55&quot;\" class=\"string\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"&quot;Followers:&quot;\" class=\"string\" /><text value=\" + followers\" /></content><interactions><interaction type=\"fillTheGap\" isDefault=\"true\"><options><option startIndex=\"21\" endIndex=\"33\" /><option startIndex=\"34\" endIndex=\"35\" /><option startIndex=\"36\" endIndex=\"45\" /></options></interaction></interactions></code><p visible-if=\"wrong\">Certifique-se de escolher <code>\"Followers:\"</code> seguido de <code>+</code> e finalmente <code>followers</code>.</p></body></html>"
          },
          {
            "title": "Display expression",
            "id": 126296,
            "contentType": "interactive",
            "images": [],
            "interactiveContent": "<!DOCTYPE html ><html><body><p>Podemos usar <code>print()</code> para ver os resultados de expressões em Swift.</p><p>Adicione uma instrução <code>print()</code> em torno da expressão.</p><code version=\"2\" codelang=\"swift\" name=\"main.swift\" visible-if=\"always\"><content><text value=\"let\" class=\"keyword\" /><text value=\" numberOfFollowers = \" /><text value=\"&quot;55&quot;\" class=\"string\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"print\" class=\"built_in\" /><text value=\"(\" /><text value=\"&quot;Followers:&quot;\" class=\"string\" /><text value=\" + numberOfFollowers);\" /></content><interactions><interaction type=\"fillTheGap\" isDefault=\"true\"><options><option startIndex=\"29\" endIndex=\"34\" /><option startIndex=\"34\" endIndex=\"35\" /><option startIndex=\"67\" endIndex=\"68\" /></options></interaction></interactions><output><content><text value=\"Followers:55\" /></content></output></code><p visible-if=\"wrong\">Certifique-se de escolher <code>print</code> seguido de <code>(</code> e finalmente <code>)</code>.</p></body></html>"
          },
          {
            "title": "Setting the result of an expression",
            "id": 126297,
            "contentType": "interactive",
            "images": [],
            "interactiveContent": "<!DOCTYPE html ><html><body><p>Como expressões se tornam valores, podemos atribuí-las a variáveis assim como fazemos com valores.</p><p>Armazene a expressão <code>\"Posts:\" + \"13\"</code> na variável <code>label</code> e exiba-a no console.</p><code version=\"2\" codelang=\"swift\" name=\"main.swift\" visible-if=\"always\"><content><text value=\"let\" class=\"keyword\" /><text value=\" label = \" /><text value=\"&quot;Posts:&quot;\" class=\"string\" /><text value=\" + \" /><text value=\"&quot;13&quot;\" class=\"string\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"print\" class=\"built_in\" /><text value=\"(label)\" /><text type=\"break\" /></content><interactions><interaction type=\"fillTheGap\" isDefault=\"true\"><options><option startIndex=\"12\" endIndex=\"20\" /><option startIndex=\"21\" endIndex=\"22\" /><option startIndex=\"23\" endIndex=\"27\" /><option startIndex=\"34\" endIndex=\"39\" /></options></interaction></interactions><output><content><text value=\"Posts:13\" /></content></output></code><p visible-if=\"wrong\">Certifique-se de escolher <code>\"Posts:\"</code> seguido de <code>+</code> e depois <code>\"13\"</code>, <code>label</code>.</p></body></html>"
