          {
            "title": "Numbers have no quotes",
            "id": 126306,
            "contentType": "interactive",
            "images": [],
            "interactiveContent": "<!DOCTYPE html ><html><body><p>Existem outros tipos de valores também. Como <strong>números</strong>, que não têm aspas duplas ao redor deles.</p><code version=\"2\" codelang=\"swift\" name=\"main.swift\" visible-if=\"always\"><content><text value=\"let\" class=\"keyword\" /><text value=\" numberOfLikes = \" /><text value=\"5\" class=\"number\" /></content><interactions><interaction type=\"fillTheGap\" isDefault=\"true\"><options><option startIndex=\"20\" endIndex=\"21\" /><option correct=\"false\"><content><text value=\"&quot;5&quot;\" /></content></option></options></interaction></interactions></code><p visible-if=\"wrong\">Certifique-se de escolher <code>5</code>.</p></body></html>"
          },
          {
            "title": "Setting numbers",
            "id": 126307,
            "contentType": "interactive",
            "images": [],
            "interactiveContent": "<!DOCTYPE html ><html><body><p>Números facilitam o acompanhamento de <strong>valores numéricos</strong>. Por exemplo, o número de curtidas em uma postagem no Facebook.</p><p>Crie uma variável <code>numberOfLikes</code> e defina-a como <code>5</code>.</p><code name=\"main.swift\" version=\"2\" codelang=\"swift\"><content><text value=\"let\" class=\"keyword\" /><text value=\" numberOfLikes = \" /><text value=\"5\" class=\"number\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"print\" class=\"built_in\" /><text value=\"(numberOfLikes)\" /></content><interactions><interaction type=\"fillTheGap\" isDefault=\"true\"><options><option startIndex=\"0\" endIndex=\"3\" /><option startIndex=\"4\" endIndex=\"17\" /><option startIndex=\"18\" endIndex=\"19\" /><option startIndex=\"20\" endIndex=\"21\" /></options></interaction></interactions><output><content><text value=\"5\" /></content></output></code><p visible-if=\"wrong\">Certifique-se de escolher <code>let</code> seguido de <code>numberOfLikes</code> e depois <code>=</code>, <code>5</code>.</p></body></html>"
          },
          {
            "title": "Addition and subtraction",
            "id": 126308,
            "contentType": "interactive",
            "images": [],
            "interactiveContent": "<!DOCTYPE html ><html><body><p>Podemos criar expressões com números também. Adicionamos números juntos com o sinal <code>+</code> e subtraímos uns dos outros com o sinal <code>-</code>.</p><p>Exiba <code>6</code> no console definindo <code>numberOfLikes</code> como <code>5 + 1</code>.</p><code version=\"2\" codelang=\"swift\" name=\"main.swift\" visible-if=\"always\"><content><text value=\"let\" class=\"keyword\" /><text value=\" numberOfLikes = \" /><text value=\"5\" class=\"number\" /><text value=\" + \" /><text value=\"1\" class=\"number\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"print\" class=\"built_in\" /><text value=\"(numberOfLikes)\" /></content><interactions><interaction type=\"fillTheGap\" isDefault=\"true\"><options><option startIndex=\"22\" endIndex=\"23\" /><option startIndex=\"24\" endIndex=\"25\" /><option correct=\"false\"><content><text value=\"-\" /></content></option></options></interaction></interactions><output><content><text value=\"6\" /></content></output></code><p visible-if=\"wrong\">Certifique-se de escolher <code>+</code> seguido de <code>1</code>.</p></body></html>"
          },
          {
            "title": "Multiplication and division",
            "id": 126309,
            "contentType": "interactive",
            "images": [],
            "interactiveContent": "<!DOCTYPE html ><html><body><p>Usamos o sinal <code>*</code> para multiplicar números e o sinal <code>/</code> para dividir números.</p><p>Transforme <code>0.5</code> em seu valor percentual multiplicando-o por <code>100</code>.</p><code version=\"2\" codelang=\"swift\" name=\"main.swift\" visible-if=\"always\"><content><text value=\"let\" class=\"keyword\" /><text value=\" percent = \" /><text value=\"0.5\" class=\"number\" /><text value=\" * \" /><text value=\"100\" class=\"number\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"print\" class=\"built_in\" /><text value=\"(percent)\" /></content><interactions><interaction type=\"fillTheGap\" isDefault=\"true\"><options><option startIndex=\"18\" endIndex=\"19\" /><option correct=\"false\"><content><text value=\"x\" /></content></option></options></interaction></interactions><output><content><text value=\"50.0\" /></content></output></code><p visible-if=\"wrong\">Certifique-se de escolher <code>*</code>.</p></body></html>"
          },
          {
            "title": "Calculating with variables",
            "id": 126310,
            "contentType": "interactive",
            "images": [],
            "interactiveContent": "<!DOCTYPE html ><html><body><p>Quando armazenamos números em variáveis, podemos usar as variáveis para cálculos também.</p><p>Adicione <code>1</code> à variável <code>numberOfSteps</code> antes de exibi-la na função print.</p><code version=\"2\" codelang=\"swift\" name=\"main.swift\" visible-if=\"always\"><content><text value=\"let\" class=\"keyword\" /><text value=\" numberOfSteps = \" /><text value=\"70\" class=\"number\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"print\" class=\"built_in\" /><text value=\"(\" /><text value=\"&quot;You're on step:&quot;\" class=\"string\" /><text value=\")\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"print\" class=\"built_in\" /><text value=\"(numberOfSteps + \" /><text value=\"1\" class=\"number\" /><text value=\")\" /></content><interactions><interaction type=\"fillTheGap\" isDefault=\"true\"><options><option startIndex=\"68\" endIndex=\"69\" /><option startIndex=\"70\" endIndex=\"71\" /><option correct=\"false\"><content><text value=\"-\" /></content></option></options></interaction></interactions><output><content><text value=\"You're on step:\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"71\" /></content></output></code><p visible-if=\"wrong\">Certifique-se de escolher <code>+</code> seguido de <code>1</code>.</p></body></html>"
          },
          {
            "title": "Calculate the total 3",
            "id": 126311,
            "contentType": "interactive",
            "images": [],
            "interactiveContent": "<!DOCTYPE html ><html><body><p>Como as expressões se tornam valores, podemos armazenar os resultados dos cálculos em variáveis.</p><p>Armazene o resultado do cálculo na variável <code>total</code>.</p><code version=\"2\" codelang=\"swift\" name=\"main.swift\" visible-if=\"always\"><content><text value=\"let\" class=\"keyword\" /><text value=\" privatePosts = \" /><text value=\"3\" class=\"number\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"let\" class=\"keyword\" /><text value=\" publicPosts = \" /><text value=\"10\" class=\"number\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"let\" class=\"keyword\" /><text value=\" total = privatePosts + publicPosts\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"print\" class=\"built_in\" /><text value=\"(\" /><text value=\"&quot;Total posts:&quot;\" class=\"string\" /><text value=\")\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"print\" class=\"built_in\" /><text value=\"(total)\" /><text type=\"break\" /></content><interactions><interaction type=\"fillTheGap\" isDefault=\"true\"><options><option startIndex=\"46\" endIndex=\"51\" /><option startIndex=\"52\" endIndex=\"53\" /><option startIndex=\"54\" endIndex=\"80\" /></options></interaction></interactions><output><content><text value=\"Total posts:\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"13\" /></content></output></code><p visible-if=\"wrong\">Certifique-se de escolher <code>total</code> seguido de <code>=</code> e finalmente <code>privatePosts + publicPosts</code>.</p></body></html>"
